{"tid":2315192,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【又上劈穿半年新高】將軍澳 山卡罅位置都1380萬上劈至新高","createTime":"2020-12-07T05:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T07:58:40.000Z","uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"847742d15be8f8be4d408a246897a2c5289278a6","tid":2315192,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:01:07.000Z","msg":"[12/7] 帝景灣本月開齋 三房1380萬沽創屋苑半年高位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受第四波新冠疫情影響，二手交投步伐略為放緩。將軍澳半新盤帝景灣，有三房單位以1380萬元易手；香港置業分區董事劉浩勤表示，上述帝景灣2座高層C室，實用面積764方呎，屬3房連儲物室間隔，以1380萬元成交，折合實呎18063元，資料顯示，上述成交價為屋苑自今年6月後，近半年來的高位。"},{"pid":"1a393497e71146bbaf2befbbb638ce7565df9d20","tid":2315192,"uid":127759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:04:06.000Z","msg":"平行時空 一邊廂 另一邊廂"},{"pid":"d7c40c81bf0c17cb958bbb8299d961556b78cec5","tid":2315192,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:04:08.000Z","msg":"點算，多創新高成交過發貼上限<br />\n<br />\n下一轉要貼old news"},{"pid":"ba5c9c73ec78d42715f84087309f3972c7d7baae","tid":2315192,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a393497e71146bbaf2befbbb638ce7565df9d20","tid":2315192,"uid":127759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:04:06.000Z","msg":"平行時空 一邊廂 另一邊廂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:05:07.000Z","msg":"創新高當然<br />\n要平行一下"},{"pid":"3563a67b7ad14a2a762841b20f925d34cc2dcbbb","tid":2315192,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:06:49.000Z","msg":"有donki好正"},{"pid":"ddcb544ddcccc29d400d9c16ece92d881588a3b8","tid":2315192,"uid":291936,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:43:20.000Z","msg":"帝景灣好近港鐵WO"},{"pid":"554afb6de04cd94ee54d01737535576cbaa3fec9","tid":2315192,"uid":57438,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:23:35.000Z","msg":"呢到都叫山卡罅"},{"pid":"05c3d305a6be59ad36910cb14dc7868e8b6db5da","tid":2315192,"uid":304431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedB